# Help Desk Voice Bot Implemention Plan

This document outlines the architecture and implementation details for the Help Desk Voice Bot.

## Proposed Architecture

The system will use a highly modular provider pattern to abstract the underlying services (LLM, Vector Store, Embeddings, STT, and TTS), making them easily swappable. We'll use the latest `langchain` and `langgraph` ecosystem for orchestration.

